{"tid":2111089,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"EA MASK、加護靈測試未能殺99.9%細菌","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T10:15:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c14d2250d0e3b30c884df3a44773f7601196774f","tid":2111089,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161130/19850172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161130%2F19850172&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFad9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=293e441c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161130%2F19850172&h=56eabe61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161130/19850172</a><br />\n<br />\nEA MASK、加護靈測試未能殺99.9%細菌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nuU7n6ZQzSPISzGcT5V-VvR4Gpc=/640x417/filters:quality(100)/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/KS5JKWCKTZFPNAT3AKJO5RX6XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnuU7n6ZQzSPISzGcT5V-VvR4Gpc%3D%2F640x417%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FKS5JKWCKTZFPNAT3AKJO5RX6XE.jpg&h=e654c64a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■空氣除菌產品EA MASK及加護靈經本報委託大學作測試，均未能做到聲稱效果。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】入冬除了要捱凍，港人也要承受北風夾雜特別多污染物之苦。日本近年興起多款空氣除菌隨身攜帶產品，標榜以二氧化氯除菌及除病毒，聲稱殺滅一米範圍內99.9%細菌。有商戶把產品引入香港，頗受家長追捧，但原來日本消費廳曾指產品未能做到聲稱效果，本報委託大學作測試，發現兩款產品未能做到聲稱殺滅或抑制逾99%細菌效果。 <br />\n<br />\n空氣除菌產品近2、3年起在香港熱賣，。。。。。。。。。。。。。因試驗在密閉空間進行，無法確定通風地方亦有效果，即令涉事17家公司停售產品。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n使用前後細菌數量相若<br />\n<br />\n消費廳名單上至少兩款產品在港有售，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報委託浸大生物系副教授賴嘉雯按產品說明作實用性測試，以機器在室內外進行8次實驗測試EA MASK除菌效果，發現使用產品前後細菌及真菌數量相若，未能做到聲稱一米內可除菌99.9%效果，「理論上係1,000粒細菌得1粒生存到。」但是否未能殺菌，她指要反覆測試才能證實，而包裝顯示產品產生0.017PPM二氧化氯，她指此濃度符合安全卻未必能殺菌，認為至少1,000PPM二氧化氯及使用30分鐘才能殺菌。<br />\n<br />\n本報借用灣仔區議員楊雪盈辦事處測試加護靈除菌效用，賴嘉雯分析發現細菌及真菌數目與在使用產品前相若，未能做到產品聲稱抑制99%細菌效果。<br />\nEA MASK。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林又引用日本防菌防黴協會研究，指在一房間釋放0.01PPM二氧化氯180分鐘可達99.9%無菌，以引證產品有效。就日本消費廳指示，他指其公司無被罰款，只被要求改善標籤，產品已重新上架。<br />\n<br />\n本報亦向生產加護靈的大幸藥品香港公司查詢，截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鍾雅宜  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/H9IUxC8xl2A59WPd0hOrXaakd5U=/791x1172/filters:quality(100)/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/TBRN6K5J626FOQLK7JMXN4XCVI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FH9IUxC8xl2A59WPd0hOrXaakd5U%3D%2F791x1172%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FTBRN6K5J626FOQLK7JMXN4XCVI.gif&h=c35eb162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6cdc5a1fe03c82c71ac88d5314796c2db22aa86","tid":2111089,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"希望多d 呢類型嘅產品，等d 智力低過80 嘅人買"},{"pid":"358c2b215e69163f88294f033a453807ff090265","tid":2111089,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"啤梨晚報 BIN C? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b799870d973bcae158e7f0db1ae5913fb07867","tid":2111089,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"小PUSH"}]}